Assignment:

# Build a python program that mimics the interest calculator of the user.

Make a simple interest calculator for the user.

Assume a scenario that user wants to invest in a specific bank.
    1. He has currently some amount to invest.
    2. He has to invest that amount for about some given years.
    3. Bank has imposed some random interest over it.

Calculate the total amount the user will get after specified year of investment, also do calculate total interest amount he will receive.

LEARN HOW TO MERGE YOUR PYTHON CODE WITH HTML -> So that through website you can interact with your python program.